<plot>David Reiner is a timid and devoted Accounts Officer who is scrambling to manage his workload. The 30 something office employee is having difficulty trying to motivate his coworkers to meet impending deadlines. His diligence and dedication always goes unnoticed and without reward. In contrast, office sweetheart, Evan Grayson (35) routinely delivers a mediocre performance, but constantly receives glowing accolades for his contributions to the company. David despises living in Evan's shadow and desperately yearns for a way to turn his own life around. In a strange and quirky turn of events, Evan's sudden and traumatic death becomes the catalyst to initiate a new beginning for David.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?425282</url></doc>
